บ This SCRIPT is to assist with Fourier refinement if simple structures.     บ
บ PHASE 1 computes phase angles from the existing model                      บ
บ PHASE 2 computes an Fobs map if R is high, a 2Fo-Fc map if intermediate    บ
บ oterwise a difference map.                                                 บ
บ PHASE 3 performs Fourier refinement or simple elimination of redundant     บ
