บ PHASE 4 assembles a molecule, reorders the atom list in decreasing         บ
บ rho values, resequences the serial numbers and displays the result         บ
บ PHASE 5 invites you to rename any of the atoms.                            บ
บ PHASES 1 to 5 are repeated until you terminate them, when the atom list    บ
บ may be reorganised to reflect atomic connectivity                          บ
